  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome all players to join our official discussion group:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ group：942540362</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord：Broken Space Traveler</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An adventure spanning dimensions, travelers from different spaces explore endless secrets in the shattered realm. In this mysterious world, you need to collect various items to strengthen yourself, upgrade your weapons, and survive in a perilous environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Characters, Strategic Survival: </strong>Dozens of travelers with unique mechanisms await your summons. Each traveler possesses their own unique survival method. Choose the role that best suits you and formulate your survival strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/3d1022397bd992e237647df68d981a0e.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/3d1022397bd992e237647df68d981a0e.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Item Combinations, Endless Possibilities: </strong>A vast array of items to select from and freely combine, creating your unique playstyle. Each combination offers a brand-new experience, filling your adventure with limitless potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Upgrades, Versatile Forms: </strong>Dozens of weapons await your unlocking. Each weapon boasts three distinct upgrade paths, granting them diverse powers. Make your choice and craft your ultimate weapon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance Travelers, Meet Demands: </strong>By collecting items or triggering events, you can empower your travelers and fulfill weapon upgrade requirements. Continuously improve your strength during your explorations, becoming the king of the shattered space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Spaces, Adjust Strategies:</strong> Surviving in the shattered space, you will gradually unlock more complete areas. Different spaces possess distinct environments and challenges. Adjust your strategies and embark on new adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join \"Broken Space Traveler\" now and embark on your cross-dimensional adventure!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome all players to join our official discussion group:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ group：942540362</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord：Broken Space Traveler</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An adventure spanning dimensions, travelers from different spaces explore endless secrets in the shattered realm. In this mysterious world, you need to collect various items to strengthen yourself, upgrade your weapons, and survive in a perilous environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Characters, Strategic Survival: </strong>Dozens of travelers with unique mechanisms await your summons. Each traveler possesses their own unique survival method. Choose the role that best suits you and formulate your survival strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/3d1022397bd992e237647df68d981a0e.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/3d1022397bd992e237647df68d981a0e.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Item Combinations, Endless Possibilities: </strong>A vast array of items to select from and freely combine, creating your unique playstyle. Each combination offers a brand-new experience, filling your adventure with limitless potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/1e47a3243e6c2997bd7891e06ce57e8c.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Upgrades, Versatile Forms: </strong>Dozens of weapons await your unlocking. Each weapon boasts three distinct upgrade paths, granting them diverse powers. Make your choice and craft your ultimate weapon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/f120ab2a9807e5cd2996952bd64e7052.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance Travelers, Meet Demands: </strong>By collecting items or triggering events, you can empower your travelers and fulfill weapon upgrade requirements. Continuously improve your strength during your explorations, becoming the king of the shattered space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/cc343ab395e8c9007cd938403e0470eb.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock Spaces, Adjust Strategies:</strong> Surviving in the shattered space, you will gradually unlock more complete areas. Different spaces possess distinct environments and challenges. Adjust your strategies and embark on new adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join \"Broken Space Traveler\" now and embark on your cross-dimensional adventure!</p>",
